query.sfwSql: SELECT CTP.TEMPLATE_ID AS iintPacketTemplateId,CTP.TEMPLATE_NAME AS istrPacketTemplateName,CTP.TEMPLATE_DESC AS istrPacketTemplateDesc, CTD.TEMPLATE_ID AS iintDocTemplateId,CTD.TEMPLATE_NAME AS istrDocTemplateName,CTD.TEMPLATE_DESC AS istrDocTemplateDesc, CTP.TEMPLATE_NAME,CTP.TEMPLATE_DESC FROM SGS_COR_TEMPLATES CTP INNER JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT CPC ON CTP.TEMPLATE_ID = CPC.PACKET_TEMPLATE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_COR_TEMPLATES CTD ON CPC.COR_TEMPLATE_ID = CTD.TEMPLATE_ID

SELECT TR.TRACKING_ID,PC.COR_PACKET_CONTENT_ID FROM SGS_COR_TRACKING TR INNER JOIN SGS_COR_TEMPLATES TM ON TR.TEMPLATE_ID = TM.TEMPLATE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT PC ON TM.TEMPLATE_ID = PC.PACKET_TEMPLATE_ID WHERE ISNULL(TM.TRACK_DETAILS_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' AND TR.TRACKING_ID = @TRACKING_ID

SELECT DISTINCT TRAC.*,PT.ACCESS_PAKET_STATUS,PT.ACCESS_TEMPLATE_NAME,ACCESS_PLAN,ACCESS_MONTHLY_CYCLE FROM SGS_COR_TRACKING TRAC INNER JOIN SGS_COR_TEMPLATES TEMP ON TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID = TEMP.TEMPLATE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT_TRACKING PT ON TRAC.TRACKING_ID = PT.TRACKING_ID WHERE ISNULL(TEMP.TRACK_DETAILS_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' AND TRAC.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID
SELECT DISTINCT TEMPLATE_NAME, TEMPLATE_DESC FROM SGS_COR_TEMPLATES WHERE TEMPLATE_TYPE_VALUE ='PCKT'

SELECT CPCT.TRACKING_ID, CTPL.TEMPLATE_ID, SP.PERSON_ID, SP.MPI_PERSON_ID AS MPID, SP.LAST_NAME+','+SP.FIRST_NAME AS NAME, SP.EMAIL_ADDRESS_1, SP.CELL_PHONE_NO, CPCT.RETIREMENT_DATE, CASE WHEN CPCT.ACCESS_TEMPLATE_NAME <> NULL OR CPCT.ACCESS_TEMPLATE_NAME <>'' THEN CPCT.ACCESS_TEMPLATE_NAME ELSE CTPL.TEMPLATE_DESC END AS TEMPLATE_DESC, CPCT.PACKET_STATUS_VALUE, CPCT.ACCESS_PAKET_STATUS as ACCESS_PAKET_STATUS, CPCT.MAILED_DATE AS MAILED_DATE, CPCT.RECEIVED_DATE, CPCT.ACCESS_MONTHLY_CYCLE, CPCT.ACCESS_PLAN, SU.USER_SERIAL_ID ANALYST_ID, (SU.FIRST_NAME + ' ' + SU.LAST_NAME) ANALYSTNAME
FROM [OPUS].[dbo].[SGS_COR_TRACKING] CT INNER JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT_TRACKING CPCT ON CT.TRACKING_ID=CPCT.TRACKING_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT CPC ON CPCT.COR_PACKET_CONTENT_ID = CPC.COR_PACKET_CONTENT_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGS_COR_TEMPLATES CTPL ON CT.TEMPLATE_ID =CTPL.TEMPLATE_ID AND CTPL.TEMPLATE_TYPE_VALUE = 'PCKT' INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON CT.PERSON_ID =SP.PERSON_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGS_USER SU ON SU.USER_SERIAL_ID = (SELECT TOP 1 ANALYST_ID FROM SGT_PERSON_CASE_ANALYST WHERE PERSON_ID = SP.PERSON_ID ORDER BY CREATED_DATE DESC)

SELECT DISTINCT RPKT.MPI_PERSON_ID, PL.PLAN_NAME, RPKT.APPLICATION_MAILED, RPKT.APPLICATION_RECEIVED, EPKT.BENEFIT_ELECTION_PACKET_MAILED, EPKT.BENEFIT_ELECTION_PACKET_RECEIVED, PAY.PAY_STATUS_DATE, PAY.PAY_STATUS FROM ( SELECT PART.MPI_PERSON_ID, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (178,182,183 ,198,210) THEN 2 --'MPI' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (187 ,194 ,185,197) THEN 1 --'IAP' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (179,200,208) THEN 8 --'L161' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (180) THEN 0 --'' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (199,211) THEN 7 --'L52' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (201,207) THEN 3 --'L600' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (202,206) THEN 4 --'L666' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (203,205) THEN 6 --'L700' ELSE 0 END AS PLAN_ID, TEMP.TEMPLATE_DESC, PT.RETIREMENT_DATE, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (178,179,180,182,183,187 ,185,197) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),MAILED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS APPLICATION_MAILED, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (178,179,180,182,183,187 ,185,197) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),RECEIVED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS APPLICATION_RECEIVED, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (198,199,200,201,202,203 ,205,206,207,208,210,211 ,194) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),MAILED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS BENEFIT_ELECTION_PACKET_MAILED, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (198,199,200,201,202,203 ,205,206,207,208,210,211 ,194) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),RECEIVED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS BENEFIT_ELECTION_PACKET_RECEIVED , TRAC.PERSON_ID, TRAC.GENERATED_DATE, TRAC.TRACKING_ID FROM SGS_COR_TRACKING TRAC INNER JOIN SGS_COR_TEMPLATES TEMP ON TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID = TEMP.TEMPLATE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT_TRACKING PT ON TRAC.TRACKING_ID = PT.TRACKING_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PART ON TRAC.PERSON_ID = PART.PERSON_ID WHERE ISNULL(TEMP.TRACK_DETAILS_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' AND TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (178,179,180,182,183,187 ,185,197 ) AND PACKET_STATUS_VALUE IN ('MOUT','CMPL') ) RPKT LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT PART.MPI_PERSON_ID, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (178,182,183 ,198,210) THEN 2 --'MPI' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (187 ,194 ,185,197) THEN 1 --'IAP' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (179,200,208) THEN 8 --'L161' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (180) THEN 0 --'' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (199,211) THEN 7 --'L52' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (201,207) THEN 3 --'L600' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (202,206) THEN 4 --'L666' WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (203,205) THEN 6 --'L700' ELSE 0 END AS PLAN_ID, TEMP.TEMPLATE_DESC, PT.RETIREMENT_DATE, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (178,179,180,182,183,187 ,185,197) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),MAILED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS APPLICATION_MAILED, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (178,179,180,182,183,187 ,185,197) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),RECEIVED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS APPLICATION_RECEIVED, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (198,199,200,201,202,203 ,205,206,207,208,210,211 ,194) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),MAILED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS BENEFIT_ELECTION_PACKET_MAILED, CASE WHEN TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN (198,199,200,201,202,203 ,205,206,207,208,210,211 ,194) THEN CONVERT(CHAR(10),RECEIVED_DATE,101) ELSE NULL END AS BENEFIT_ELECTION_PACKET_RECEIVED , TRAC.PERSON_ID, TRAC.GENERATED_DATE FROM SGS_COR_TRACKING TRAC INNER JOIN SGS_COR_TEMPLATES TEMP ON TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID = TEMP.TEMPLATE_ID INNER JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT_TRACKING PT ON TRAC.TRACKING_ID = PT.TRACKING_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON PART ON TRAC.PERSON_ID = PART.PERSON_ID WHERE ISNULL(TEMP.TRACK_DETAILS_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' AND TRAC.TEMPLATE_ID IN ( 198,199,200,201,202,203 ,205,206,207,208,210,211 ,194) AND PACKET_STATUS_VALUE IN ('MOUT','CMPL') ) EPKT ON (RPKT.PERSON_ID = EPKT.PERSON_ID AND RPKT.RETIREMENT_DATE = EPKT.RETIREMENT_DATE AND RPKT.PLAN_ID = EPKT.PLAN_ID) LEFT OUTER JOIN ( SELECT CONVERT(CHAR(10),BA.APPLICATION_RECEIVED_DATE,101) AS APP_RECEIVED, CONVERT(CHAR(10),BA.MODIFIED_DATE,101) AS APP_UPDATED , BA.APPLICATION_STATUS_VALUE AS APP_STATUS, CONVERT(CHAR(10),PAS.MODIFIED_DATE,101) AS PAY_STATUS_DATE , CASE WHEN PAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'APRD' THEN 'Scheduled' WHEN PAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'CMPL' AND ISNULL(PA.ADJUSTMENT_PAYMENT_ELIGIBLE_FLAG,'N') = 'Y' THEN 'Scheduled' WHEN PAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'CMPL' AND DATEADD(D,5,(select top(1) PAYMENT_DATE from SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER where PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID order by PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID desc)) >= GETDATE() THEN 'Scheduled' WHEN PAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'CMPL' THEN 'Payment Completed' WHEN PAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'RECV' THEN 'Receiving' WHEN PAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'SPND' THEN 'Receiving' WHEN PAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'REVW' THEN 'Review' ELSE '' END AS PAY_STATUS, PB.PLAN_ID , BA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID AS APP_ID , BA.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE , ISNULL(BA.RETIREMENT_DATE, BA.WITHDRAWAL_DATE) AS RETIREMENT_DATE , PA.PERSON_ID, PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_PERSON PART INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION BA ON PART.PERSON_ID = BA.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL BAD ON BA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID = BAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR PB ON BAD.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = PB.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA ON PART.PERSON_ID = PA.PERSON_ID AND BAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = PA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS PAS ON PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID = (SELECT MAX(PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS_ID) FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS WHERE PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID) WHERE PAS.STATUS_VALUE <> 'CNCL' AND ISNULL(PA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG,'N') = 'N' AND ((PB.PLAN_ID <> 1 AND BA.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RTMT','DSBL')) OR (PB.PLAN_ID = 1 AND BA.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RTMT','DSBL','WDRL')) ) ) PAY ON ( (RPKT.PERSON_ID = PAY.PERSON_ID AND RPKT.RETIREMENT_DATE = PAY.RETIREMENT_DATE AND RPKT.PLAN_ID = PAY.PLAN_ID) OR (RPKT.PERSON_ID = PAY.PERSON_ID AND RPKT.RETIREMENT_DATE = PAY.RETIREMENT_DATE AND PAY.PLAN_ID = 1) OR (EPKT.PERSON_ID = PAY.PERSON_ID AND EPKT.RETIREMENT_DATE = PAY.RETIREMENT_DATE AND EPKT.PLAN_ID = PAY.PLAN_ID) ) INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN PL ON ( ISNULL(ISNULL(PAY.PLAN_ID, EPKT.PLAN_ID),RPKT.PLAN_ID) = PL.PLAN_ID) WHERE RPKT.MPI_PERSON_ID = @MPI_PERSON_ID ORDER BY RPKT.MPI_PERSON_ID, RPKT.APPLICATION_MAILED

SELECT SP.MPI_PERSON_ID , SP.PERSON_ID, PT.* FROM SGS_COR_TRACKING AS SCT JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SP.PERSON_ID = SCT.PERSON_ID JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT_TRACKING PT ON SCT.TRACKING_ID = PT.TRACKING_ID WHERE PT.ACCESS_TEMPLATE_NAME IS NULL AND PACKET_STATUS_VALUE <> 'CNCL' AND SCT.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SCT.TRACKING_ID <> @TRACKING_ID

SELECT SP.MPI_PERSON_ID , SP.PERSON_ID, SCT.TRACKING_ID,pt.COR_PACKET_CONTENT_ID,pt.COR_PACKET_CONTENT_TRACKING_ID,pt.PACKET_STATUS_VALUE, SCT.TEMPLATE_ID FROM SGS_COR_TRACKING AS SCT JOIN SGT_PERSON SP ON SP.PERSON_ID = SCT.PERSON_ID JOIN SGS_COR_PACKET_CONTENT_TRACKING PT ON SCT.TRACKING_ID = PT.TRACKING_ID WHERE PT.ACCESS_TEMPLATE_NAME IS NULL AND PACKET_STATUS_VALUE <> 'CNCL' AND SCT.PERSON_ID =@PersonId
